'''Greel Wood Logging Corporation''', founded by [[Meysen Kayson]], was a [[Wood/Legends|wood]]-harvesting corporation. It harvested luxury [[Greel wood/Legends|greel wood]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] [[Pii III]] and [[Pii IV]] in the [[Arkanis sector/Legends|Araknis sector]]. As part of its operations, the corporation produced the [[TreeFelling vibrosaw]], and worked with [[Industrial Automaton/Legends|Industrial Automaton]] to create the [[FLR-series Logger Droid|FLR "Lumberdroid."]]

